window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Jacob now has seven newly minted Demon Lords, but his plate is still plenty full.&nbsp;</p> <p>The Unholy Trio of Baphomet, Gressil, and Beelzebub are still out to kill him, so Jake’s gotta stay one step ahead of the game.&nbsp;</p> <p>Good thing he has dozens of new succubi all vying to become his next Demon Lords.&nbsp;</p> <p>The question is which beautiful demon-woman will win \"Who wants to be Jakey’s succubus?\"</p>"; 
